{"id": "1527735203366174740", "channel_id": "1527735203366174740", "author_id": "333242078475714560", "author_name": "diwireal", "content": "Hi, everyone! Looking for some advice.\n\nAfter 1.5 months, I finally managed to build 5 teams for a 300+ D-Tide clear. Everything seems to be working pretty well (2-3 alerts), but there are probably some obvious improvements I'm missing. Maybe there are better team/gear setups?\nI'd also like some advice on who to build next and what teams to work toward with my current roster. The long-term goal is to eventually build a solid roster of 10 teams for D-Tide.\n\nAnother thing I'm wondering about is the best use for my duplicates. Right now I have 4 character dupes and 4 wheel dupes. I'm leaning toward investing evenly the character dupes into Corpo and Pontos, and the wheel dupes into Caster and Pontos. Not sure if that's the best use of them, though. Does that make sense, or would you recommend something else?", "timestamp": "2026-07-17T17:54:16.430000+00:00", "thread_id": "1527735203366174740", "attachments": [{"id": "1527735204020490491", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1350116, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1527735203366174740/1527735204020490491/image.png?ex=6a5c6688&is=6a5b1508&hm=ffc5ce0aa93b0c71b6b7edf20fee3630ec729320069bd52c17d80cff2efb432a&"}, {"id": "1527735204440178709", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1339953, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1527735203366174740/1527735204440178709/image.png?ex=6a5c6688&is=6a5b1508&hm=80070d66c76a6bc5b2a436b5980fc6119c413b3afeb74b9b2d410e97ac52e874&"}, {"id": "1527735204876259328", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1277193, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1527735203366174740/1527735204876259328/image.png?ex=6a5c6688&is=6a5b1508&hm=884526549fac5f902b9acddbd89c161efc9a454eaca36d523fab08f3d00df8f5&"}, {"id": "1527735205442621501", "filename": "image.png